He might.

19:36.080 --> 19:38.059
If we see him again.

19:40.800 --> 19:45.544
It was not without difficulty
that my mother secured your invitation.

19:45.720 --> 19:47.506
I'm obliged to her.

19:48.560 --> 19:52.542
